org.shared.util

Interface DynamicArray<T extends DynamicArray<T,V,E>,V,E>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the parameterization lower bounded by DynamicArray itself.
    V - the storage array type.
    E - the component type.
    All Superinterfaces:
    Cloneable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DynamicDoubleArray, DynamicIntArray, DynamicLongArray, DynamicObjectArray

    public interface DynamicArray<T extends DynamicArray<T,V,E>,V,E>
extends Cloneable
    Defines an array that can grow and shrink dynamically.
